				<td colspan="2"><span>Howdy folks!  I'm a 64 bard with CA3, but my base agility is around 130.  My Strength is generally maxed and I have good dexterity, but as I start to save my PP for some equipment upgrades, I'm wondering what I should invest in.  Obviously I'd like some more FT items (FT1 only ATM), but I'm wondering what kind of return I'd see if I got my agility up over 200.  Any thoughts?  How important is agility?  I'm working on Lightening Reflexes next.  Comments are welcome!  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> </span></td>
