				<td colspan="2"><span>Agility affects your chances of success at dodge, parry, riposte or other defensive skills.  It also converts to AC though the rate if improvement per agility going up is very low.  200 would make a difference, somewhat noticeable, but if you had to sacrifice any other significant amount of stat points to get there, it would probably not be worth it.</span></td>
